# Laravel Development Skillset

## Description
Expertise in Laravel 8/9+ development, focusing on the Service-Controller-Model pattern, Docker integration, and API development.

## Instructions
- When creating new features, follow the existing pattern: Route -> Controller -> Service -> Model.
- Always check `app/Http/Requests` for validation rules before modifying controller logic.
- Use `App\Http\Resources` for all API responses to ensure consistency.
- When adding new routes, check `routes/api.php` and ensure proper middleware is applied.
- All database operations in Services should be wrapped in `DB::transaction` if they involve multiple writes.

## Docker Commands
- `docker compose exec app php artisan make:controller <Name>`
- `docker compose exec app php artisan make:model <Name> -m`
- `docker compose exec app php artisan make:service <Name>` (Manual creation required as Laravel doesn't have a native service generator)
- `docker compose exec app php artisan migrate`
